highlights.text: “Houdini” by Eminem is the highest new entry on Top Songs Israel at #14.
“סלינה” by Peer Tasi is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 106 spots at #76.
Omer Adam has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “ראיתי עולם” is the highest at #1.
“לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 326 weeks straight.
